extension_letter.template:
Dear {{applicant_name}},

Re: FOI Request {{tracking_number}}

We are writing to inform you that we require an extension of time to respond to your request under Section 10 of the Freedom of Information and Protection of Privacy Act.

Reason for extension: {{extension_reason}}

The new response date is {{new_due_date}}. This represents an extension of {{extension_days}} calendar days from the original deadline.

If you have any questions about this extension, please contact us at {{contact_email}}.

Sincerely,
{{organization_name}}
Freedom of Information Office

response_letter.template:
Dear {{applicant_name}},

Re: FOI Request {{tracking_number}}

Please find enclosed {{document_count}} document(s) responsive to your request dated {{request_date}}.

{{redaction_summary}}

You have the right to request a review of this decision by the Information and Privacy Commissioner of British Columbia within 30 business days of receiving this response. For more information, please visit www.oipc.bc.ca.

If you have any questions about this response, please contact us at {{contact_email}}.

Sincerely,
{{organization_name}}
Freedom of Information Office

fee_estimate.template:
Dear {{applicant_name}},

Re: FOI Request {{tracking_number}}

The estimated fee for processing your request is ${{estimated_fee}} CAD.

This estimate includes:
- Search time: ${{search_fee}}
- Preparation time: ${{prep_fee}}
- Copying: ${{copy_fee}}

Fees are calculated according to the FIPPA Regulation fee schedule in effect at the time of the request. The first three hours of search and retrieval time are free for general applicants.

Please confirm within 30 days if you wish to proceed with this request. If you believe you qualify for a fee waiver under s.75(5), please provide supporting documentation.

Sincerely,
{{organization_name}}
Freedom of Information Office

