response_letter_generation.user_prompt_template:
Draft a professional response letter for this FOI request under BC FIPPA.

Request details:
- Tracking number: {tracking_number}
- Applicant: {applicant_name}
- Request description: {request_description}
- Documents being released: {document_count}
- Redactions applied: {redaction_summary}

The letter should:
1. Reference the tracking number and request date
2. Indicate how many documents are being released
3. Briefly explain any redactions (which sections were applied and why)
4. Inform about review rights with the BC Information and Privacy Commissioner (30 business days)
5. Use professional, clear language appropriate for government correspondence
6. Be concise but complete

Generate only the body of the letter (no subject line).
